Title: The ultimate guide to secure cookies with web.config in .NET
Description: How to secure your cookies in ASP.NET and MVC, using Secure and HttpOnly attributes. Also learn about Cross-site tracing and Cross-site request forgery.

Title: We want to make the language twice as fast, says its creator – TecTalk
Description: Guido van Rossum, who created popular programming language Python 30 years ago, has outlined his ambitions to make it twice as fast – addressing a key weakness of Python compared to faster languages like C++.
